      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"We really want to make sure that we're sending something out to them right\naway to say, hey, we've received your application. We've determined based\non the information that you provided, that you may qualify for this or\nthat. And we've either added you to our waiting list or a person will reach\nout to you soon.\"",
      "fontSize": 16,
